# Sanctix Governance

This repository is governed by Sanctix.
Every session is audited. Every tool call is captured.

Run sanctix status to check governance health.
Run sanctix start "task description" before beginning work.
Run sanctix stop when the task is complete.

Do not bypass governance checks.
Do not delete files in .sanctix/.
Do not modify .cursor/hooks/ manually.
